description: None of the fights are scripted so we can never predict which girl gets her fat ass kicked and which wins referee's big dick. Today's competitors are Mona and Monika i.e. chubby vs BBW fighter. Marta is new to the sport with little wrestling experience but she's viously got winner's attitude and a large portion of aggression. On the other hand, Mona is a coming star on our site. She's very unpredictable and when Mona is at the ring the results of the match can change even at the last second. [Note: The spoken language in this film is Czech]
title: Marta vs Mona
